{"service_name": "Technical communication services for software projects", "service_id": "7518608385058220", "company_name": "Scroll LLP", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Scroll LLP\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Technical communication services for software projects\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    Scroll can manage all content in alignment with industry best practices of single-sourcing content, using intelligent content principles. This facilitates the use of content within a software system, on sites, in knowledge bases, on devices, in the appropriate languages. We use specialty software to create, deliver and maintain content.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Use specialty software eg Help Authoring Tool (HAT) \u2022\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Determine the content needs of end users\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Design transactional content, embedded assistance, and related help topics\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Match medium to audience (embedded assistance, help topics, videos, infographics)\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Determine when photographs, drawings, diagrams, animation, charts increase user comprehension\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Standardise content terminology across platforms and media\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Gather usage data to improve UX, user comprehension, conversion rates\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Create a transition plan for post-launch maintenance of content\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Design BAU maintenance plans for source language and target languages\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Content can be published to multiple devices and formats\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     No need to duplicate content or effort\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Write once, publish many times\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Adapt content to multiple user groups or markets more efficiently\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Content is adapted iteratively in response to user feedback\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     The content is structurally and semantically rich\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     The content is more effective for processing by software systems\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Better findability by search engines and on-site search\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3450 to \u00a3775 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Including VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Education pricing available\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Termination costs apply\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92710/7518608385058220-pricing-document-2015-10-06-1241.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92710/7518608385058220-sfia-rate-card-2015-10-06-1241.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92710/7518608385058220-service-definition-document-2015-10-06-1241.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/92710/7518608385058220-terms-and-conditions-2015-10-06-1241.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Terms and conditions\n      </a>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Framework\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"external-link-default\">\n     <a href=\"http://ccs-agreements.cabinetoffice.gov.uk/contracts/rm1557vii\" rel=\"external\">\n      G-Cloud 7\n     </a>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Service ID\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"service-id\">\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      7518\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      6083\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      8505\n     </span>\n     <span class=\"service-id-chunk\">\n      8220\n     </span>\n    </div>\n    <h2 class=\"sidebar-heading\">\n     Contact\n    </h2>\n    <div class=\"contact-details\" itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Organization\">\n     <p class=\"contact-details-organisation\">\n      <span itemprop=\"name\">\n       Scroll LLP\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-details-block\">\n      <span itemscope=\"\" itemtype=\"http://schema.org/Person\">\n       <span itemprop=\"name\">\n        Hetty Meyric Hughes\n       </span>\n      </span>\n     </p>\n     <p class=\"contact-detail